    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what i mean is, it's not just that i'm tired. it feels like there's just a defect in me. like the more i try to fix it, the more i realize that some people are just meant to struggle and that maybe i'm just a lost cause. is it really okay to just... stop trying to get better?",
